# Frontend Conventions — EVNICT Standard
> QĐ-TTPM Điều 8, Mục 8.6 | Angular + PrimeNG

## RF01: No Inline Styles
- Tất cả styles trong .scss — KHÔNG style="..." hoặc [style.x]
- Dùng CSS classes, [class.active]="condition"

## RF02: Component Reuse
- Kiểm tra PrimeNG (p-table, p-dialog, p-dropdown) trước khi tạo mới
- Component dùng ≥2 nơi → đặt trong shared/

## RF03: No Hardcoded Text / i18n
- ALL text qua `{{ 'key' | translate }}` (ngx-translate)
- Labels, messages, tooltips, placeholders → translate

## RF04: Accessibility
- img PHẢI có alt. Form field PHẢI có label/aria-label.
- Interactive elements PHẢI có tabindex. Color contrast ≥ 4.5:1

## RF05: No Direct DOM
- KHÔNG document.getElementById() / querySelector()
- Dùng @ViewChild, Renderer2, template bindings

## RF06: Responsive
- Desktop (≥1200), Tablet (768-1199), Mobile (≤767)
- PrimeNG Grid: `class="col-12 md:col-6 lg:col-4"`
- Table: `[scrollable]="true" responsiveLayout="scroll"`

## Angular Conventions
- File: `{name}.component.ts`, `{name}.service.ts`, `{name}.module.ts`
- Component order: Decorators → Public props → Private → Constructor → Lifecycle → Public methods → Private methods
- RxJS: takeUntil(destroy$) hoặc async pipe — KHÔNG subscribe leak
- Service: `@Injectable({ providedIn: 'root' })`, base URL từ environment

## Naming
- Selector prefix: `app-`, File: `customer-list.component.ts`
- Feature path: `src/app/features/{module}/`, Shared: `src/app/shared/`
